Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.store

Class BatchingNeoStores

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.store.BatchingNeoStores
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, MemoryStatsVisitor.Visitable
    public class BatchingNeoStores
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable, MemoryStatsVisitor.Visitable
    Creator and accessor of NeoStores with some logic to provide very batch friendly services to the NeoStores when instantiating it. Different services for specific purposes.

      • pruneAndOpenExistingStore

        public void pruneAndOpenExistingStore​(Predicate<StoreType> mainStoresToKeep,
                                      Predicate<StoreType> tempStoresToKeep)
                               throws IOException
        Called when expecting a previous attempt/state of a database to open, where some store files should be kept, but others deleted. All temporary stores will be deleted in this call.
        Parameters:
        mainStoresToKeep - Predicate controlling which files to keep, i.e. true means keep, false means delete.
        tempStoresToKeep - Predicate controlling which files to keep, i.e. true means keep, false means delete.
        Throws:
        IOException
